    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>

        
            <div rend="parallel">
                <lg xml:id="Aink404">
                    <l>vāṇuta larivai makaṉmulai yūṭṭat</l>
                    <l>tāṉavaḷ ciṟupuṟaṅ kavaiyiṉa ṉaṉṟu</l>
                    <l>naṟumpūn taṇpuṟa vaṇinta</l>
                    <l>kuṟumpal poṟaiya nāṭukiḻa vōṉē.</l>
                </lg>
                <p xml:lang="en">
                    While the young woman with the bright forehead nursed [her] son at her chest,
                    that lord of the land with many small hills covered in cool forests with lovely
                    fragrant flowers, he embraced the small of her back.
                </p>
            </div>
